*Covece*, ono je jako ludo. (That person is really crazy.)
Oni su *covece* razdelili u dve grupe. (They divided the people into two groups.)
*Coveka* je zaposlio u svoju firmu. (He hired a man into his company.)
Mislio je da ce *coveka* prihvatiti. (He thought that he will be accepted.)
Bila je ljubazna prema svakom *coveku*. (She was kind to every person.)
Oni su ispratili *coveka* do vrata. (They escorted the man to the door.)